Guys, come here.

1384
01:41:38,303 --> 01:41:39,386
AP, come here.

1385
01:41:42,178 --> 01:41:45,219
See the reflection
of this rock on the water.

1386
01:41:49,636 --> 01:41:50,636
Rock?

1387
