Fine. Forget about your fees.

1402
01:42:24,969 --> 01:42:25,761
Let's go...

1403
01:42:26,386 --> 01:42:27,719
How can I forget about it?

1404
01:42:27,803 --> 01:42:29,386
I've kept an account of everything.
AP is coming...

1405
